  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized prospective study to evaluate the effectiveness of a family-based
      intervention using activity-monitors (I.e. Fitbits) in children and adolescents aged 8-18
      years with a BMI greater than or equal to 95%ile who attend the Cleveland Clinic
      multidisciplinary &quot;Be Well&quot; pediatric obesity clinic.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
